{"tid":1557652,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國駐俄大使指香港發生泯滅人性暴行　稱支持警方執法","createTime":"2019-09-10T08:01:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T09:43:52.000Z","uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"0ca3089e990bd767de8dc69aedaed801d6c8b8a9","tid":1557652,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:01:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1479825_1_L_20190910154945.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1479825_1_L_20190910154945.jpg&h=16b2a8e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1479825-20190910.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1479825-20190910.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdDycuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=7ad99bfb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1479825-20190910.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=81962f2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1479825-20190910.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n2019-09-10 HKT 15:43<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國駐俄大使張漢暉說，以美國為首的部分西方國家，罔顧中方嚴正立場，罔顧國際法及國際關係基本準則，屢次對香港事務指手畫腳，粗暴干涉中國內政，中方對此堅決反對。<br />\n<br />\n張漢暉接受俄羅斯衛星通訊社專訪，被問到對香港局勢看法時又形容，從傳媒看到泯滅人性、令人髮指的極端暴行。他說沒有法治的「民主」和沒有秩序的「自由」，只會導致無政府主義和社會動亂，北京將繼續堅定支持香港特區政府依法施政，堅定支持香港警方嚴正執法。<br />\n<br />\n張漢暉說中俄在有關問題上互相支持，說明雙方對維護國家主權和安全、維護社會穩定和秩序等方面，有著共同的利益和訴求。"},{"pid":"45257139a3f14c019a0f2d28b1184fb59410e99a","tid":1557652,"uid":121409,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:02:48.000Z","msg":"開始唔掂要契哥呵返<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be959af181df963232ed6204f342b255d6204703","tid":1557652,"uid":245292,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:03:40.000Z","msg":"自古以來海參崴屬於???"},{"pid":"6189f4ce73240ce4ed95